           --> SC Simplified Chinese 将...添加到  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 将...附加到 
 
add-on n (optional extra feature)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 附加功能 TC Traditional Chinese 附加功能  
 -- The software has lots of add-ons.
 
add-on n (additional charge)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 附加费用 TC Traditional Chinese 附加費用  
 -- The bill includes add-ons.
 
add-on adj (feature: optional, extra)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 附加的，附带的 fù jiā de ，fù dài de TC Traditional Chinese 附加的  (功能)
 -- The program provides many add-on features.
 
adjudicate on [sth] vi + prep (settle a dispute)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 裁决, 审判  
 
advise [sb] on [sth] vtr + prep (counsel on)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 就某事给某人提供建议  
 -- He was hired to advise the Queen on matters of state.
 -- 他被雇来就国事向女王谏言献策。
 
advise [sb] on [sth] vtr + prep (warn about or recommend)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 就某事向某人提出建议  
 -- Eddie advised us on the best restaurants to visit.
 
aggression on [sth/sb] n (attack, infringement)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 攻击 gōng jī TC Traditional Chinese 攻擊  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 侵犯 gōng jī，qīn fàn TC Traditional Chinese 侵犯 
 -- This recent violence against a minority is an aggression on our society as a whole.
 -- 最近针对少数族裔的暴力事件是对对我们整个社会的一种侵犯。
 
agree with [sb] about [sth], agree with [sb] on [sth] v expr (have same opinion about)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 在某事方面同意某人的观点  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 赞同某人所做的某事 
 -- We all agreed with Jack about the colour of the new chairs.
 -- 我们一致赞同杰克为新椅子选的颜色。
 
agree on [sth] vi + prep (decide mutually)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 在…问题上意见统一 zài wèn tí shàng yì jiàn tǒng yī  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 就…达成一致 zài wèn tí shàng yì jiàn tǒng yī，jiù … dá chéng yí zhì 
 -- Both sides agreed on a truce.
 -- 交战双方都同意停战。
 
agree on terms v expr (decide conditions)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 就条款达成一致意见 jiù tiáo kuǎn dá chéng yí zhì yì jiàn  
 -- The two companies agreed on terms and the contract was signed.
 -- 两家公司就条款达成一致，签订了合同。
 
